## Public Member Functions

### addBlockToCycle() {#a153679add0de628fdec2583dfd0769f2}

<MemberDefinition
  template={<>template &lt;typename ContextT&gt;</>}
  prototype={<>void llvm::GenericCycleInfo&lt; ContextT &gt;::addBlockToCycle (<a href="#aec1c9d49a4d0b62899f66e685df5bcc2">BlockT</a> &#42; Block, <a href="#a9e8490b86453fd5197b0890c7c4b2b7e">CycleT</a> &#42; Cycle)</>}>
Assumes that <code><a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#a60dc5ae8be8d73033ce099677e645b9b">Cycle</a></code> is the innermost cycle containing <code>Block</code>.

<code>Block</code> will be appended to <code><a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#a60dc5ae8be8d73033ce099677e645b9b">Cycle</a></code> and all of its parent cycles. <code>Block</code> will be added to BlockMap with <code><a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#a60dc5ae8be8d73033ce099677e645b9b">Cycle</a></code> and BlockMapTopLevel with <code><a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#a60dc5ae8be8d73033ce099677e645b9b">Cycle</a>&#39;s</code> top level parent cycle.

Declaration at line <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/adt/genericcycleinfo-h/#l00308">308</a> of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/adt/genericcycleinfo-h">GenericCycleInfo.h</a>, definition at line <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/adt/genericcycleimpl-h/#l00312">312</a> of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/adt/genericcycleimpl-h">GenericCycleImpl.h</a>.
